info: Rating, 5 stars,  · April 2024,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: Modern and well equipped furniture and appliances. We had enjoyable stay. Host Hossain and caretaker was good in communication. I would like to stay again if needed.

The house was not fully Airbnb-compliant. only bar soap and kitchen appliances no shampoo or no Breakfast item. only one towel. The best part was that Hot water was available. Most Airbnb in Bangladesh do not comply with the standard. average This is a good home. I am not very familiar with the area. my friends and family told me it wasn't a safe area. because it was surrounded by a project camp. I did not see any danger myself. it's a new beautiful home. The caretaker was a great guy. very helpful nice and polite. since I stayed there for 4 days, now I know a little more about the area than before I will be back near future. nice and secure home. In most of the places, I stayed hot water was red. This house is perfect for people living abroad.
